text: "Bungle in the Jungle" is a 1974 song by British progressive rock band Jethro Tull and was taken from their seventh studio album War Child. It went to number 12 in the United States, number 4 in Canada and number 32 in Australia. ==References== Category:1974 songs Category:Progressive rock songs Category:Jethro Tull (band) songs
title: Bungle in the Jungle
